  <!-- Applications -->
  <h2 id="applications">Applications</h2>

  <p>
    The Alfa Laval MAB-103 is a purifier-type disc-stack centrifuge. It is designed to separate water (moisture) and fine sediment from mineral oil and lubricating oil. It is primarily used for purifying fuels such as <a href="/diesel-centrifuge/">diesel</a>, kerosene, etc.
  </p>
  <p>
    The MAB-103 is also used for separating water and fine sediment from <a href="/lube-oil-centrifuge/">lubricating oil</a>, <a href="/hydraulic-oil-centrifuge/">hydraulic oil</a>, and other mineral oils.
  </p>

